headline: Erie Strategic Ventures invests in Atomic and Feathery to advance innovation in insurance and financial technology
summary: Erie Strategic Ventures, the venture capital arm of Erie Insurance (ERIE), today announced investments in two new portfolio companies: Atomic and Feathery.

headline: Erie Indemnity Earnings Preview: What to Expect
summary: Erie Indemnity is expected to release its fiscal third-quarter earnings later this month, and analysts project a double-digit earnings growth.
